{
  "text": "In this paper we derive in Section 2 for the minimax results mentioned in relations [CITATION_1] up to (10) a necessary and sufficient condition on the function f and the sets A and B. In section 3 we apply the minimax results of Section 2 to derive results for the special case of Lagrangian duality in optimization.",
